title: Best banana bread
ingredients: ['110g butter', '220g brown sugar', '1 egg, beaten', '3 large ripe bananas, mashed', '250g plain flour', '2 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/4 teaspoon nutmeg', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '120ml milk', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract']
